Package: tayloR
Type: Package
Title: Taylor Series Expansion
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Im-a", "scRiptR", , "eldoradotradez@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package performs the Taylor Series Expansion for any given 
  single variable function. It also includes a remainder calculation function
  as well as the Taylor Remainder plot.
